name: Superstructure //2
description:
'Superstructure' is a lyrical heroine born in a machine whose visual language is similar to its creator. With this series I want to address how the image is formed - the gradual fleshing out of form-information in the shape of colour and spatial patterns, bringing together architecture and glitch.

3000x4000

Artwork by pavelskyi
